OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister has told ITV
OL,7,FNews that he came under "huge
OL,8,Fpressure" whilst finalising a deal to
OL,9,Fbuild the island's new hospital.
OL,11,FSenator Tom Binet has criticised the
OL,12,Fmachinery of government for slowing
OL,13,Fthe timeline down, as a contract was
OL,14,Fsigned just two days before the
OL,15,Felection after months of negotiation
OL,16,Fand years of debate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FAt the time, the Department of Health
OL,7,Fand Social Care said that the deal was
OL,8,F"within the financial envelope agreed
OL,9,Fby the States Assembly" - referring to
OL,10,Fthe #710 million project budget.
OL,12,FHowever, that funding will also have
OL,13,Fto pay for the development of two
OL,14,Fother "major sites" - the Kensington
OL,15,FPlace ambulance station and St Saviour
OL,16,FHealth Village - which were not
OL,17,Fincluded under this contract.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FWhen announced, the department would
OL,7,Fnot say how much the hospital contract
OL,8,Fwith Bouygues UK cost, citing the
OL,9,Freporting restrictions of an election
OL,10,Fperiod.
OL,12,FA month later, Senator Binet said he
OL,13,Fhad not yet considered when more
OL,14,Finformation will be published but
OL,15,Finsists that some details will
OL,16,Feventually be released.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FThe Minister also rebuffed claims that
OL,7,Fhe had not provided sufficient
OL,8,Finformation to the previous Council of
OL,9,FMinisters on the contents of the
OL,10,Fcontract and the timing of its signing.
OL,12,FHe told ITV News that the detail he
OL,13,Fgave them was "very comprehensive" and
OL,14,Fthat "they were left in absolutely no
OL,15,Fdoubt as to what the key issues were".
OL,17,FSenator Binet stressed that the timing
OL,18,Fof the announcement, two days before
OL,19,Flast month's election, was crucial.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FHe warned that the construction
OL,7,Fcompany may have lost trust in the
OL,8,FGovernment if it had failed to meet
OL,9,Fthe agreed timeline.
OL,11,FThe Health Minister also made striking
OL,12,Fcritiques of Comptroller and Auditor
OL,13,FGeneral Lynn Pamment.
OL,15,FSenator Binet claimed she "intervened
OL,16,Fvery, very heavy handedly" and that he
OL,17,Fcame under pressure to complete due
OL,18,Fdiligence before the contract was
OL,19,Fsigned, something he disagreed with.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,F"I don't think it was reasonable for
OL,7,Fanybody to have been put under the
OL,8,Fpressure that I was put under", he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"The bit that disturbed me most was
OL,12,Ftowards the end when, if I'd have
OL,13,Fbowed to the pressure, I'd have left
OL,14,Fsigning until after the election."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FThe hospital has been under increased
OL,7,Fscrutiny in recent months after dozens
OL,8,Fof patients had operations cancelled
OL,9,Fin heatwaves. The Medical Director
OL,10,Fpointed to broken air conditioning and
OL,11,Fother issues due, in part, to "older
OL,12,Ffacilities".
OL,14,FMary Venturini is Chair of the
OL,15,Fcampaign group Friends of Our New
OL,16,FHospital. Speaking to ITV News, she
OL,17,Fvoiced concerns about the lack of
OL,18,Finformation in the public domain.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,F"We know very very little", she said.
OL,7,F"We don't even know the price of the
OL,8,Fcontract ... I would just love to see
OL,9,Fa date for all of this to begin."
OL,11,FWhen contacted for comment, Ms
OL,12,FPamment's office referred ITV Channel
OL,13,Fto the annual Audit Plan, released in
OL,14,FJanuary. This year's will include an
OL,15,Fanalysis of the redeveloping of
OL,16,Fhospital sites.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
