OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783703991
OL,3,CHealth Minister criticises Civil
OL,4,CService delays in hospital project
OL,6,FThey also pointed out that the
OL,7,FComptroller and Auditor General
OL,8,Foperates "under the Comptroller and
OL,9,FAuditor General (Jersey) Law 2014 and
OL,10,Fin accordance with a published Code of
OL,11,FAudit Practice issued under that Law".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
